node.text:
N E W  I N 🌈

We’re so excited to share these Mama Designs swaddles, duvet sets & Babasacs with you. Head to stories to hear more about the multi tog design of this clever sleeping bag 💤 It’s perfect for those months when the weather can’t make its mind up & you switch between bed socks & having the fan on, on the daily 🙌 Peace of mind whether it’s chilly OR toasty

TAP to shop

node.text:
M A I L E G

Fun fact: did you know this magical Danish toy brand is pronounced “my lie”? 

Have you started your collection yet?? From mice to bunnies, monkeys, hedgehogs & pandas too, you’re sure to find a new friend. Or two. Or… you get the picture ♥️ 

TAP to shop our favourites

#maileg #playroomfun #maileglove #mailegworld #fun #mailegmouse #mailegmice #kidsroom #toys #toysofinstagram #mailegtoys #playroominspo #imaginativeplay #playtime #playroomdecor #playroomgoals #reelitfeelit #scandikidsroom #playroomfun #reels #mousehouse #dollshouse #kidsinteriorlove #kidsroom #kidsinterior #nordickidsliving #kinderzimmerdeko #fyp #barnrum #mykidsfavourites

U N D E R  T H E  S E A

Can we have a show of hands from all the Little Mermaid fans 🙋🙋🙋 absolute ocean goals right here 🐋🦀🐚 My inner Ariel is swooning!

Swipe to see the Enzo canopy doing its best impression of a jellyfish 👉👉

📷 thanks to the wonderful @banish_the_beige_
